23DecodeTargetIndication
24Dti(int sid, int tid, const ScalableVideoController::LayerFrameConfig& config) {
25 if (config.IsKeyframe()) {
26 RTC_DCHECK_EQ(config.TemporalId(), 0);
27 return sid < config.SpatialId() ? DecodeTargetIndication::kNotPresent
28 : DecodeTargetIndication::kSwitch;
29 }
30
31 if (sid != config.SpatialId() || tid < config.TemporalId()) {
32 return DecodeTargetIndication::kNotPresent;
33 }
34 if (tid == config.TemporalId() && tid > 0) {
35 return DecodeTargetIndication::kDiscardable;
36 }
37 return DecodeTargetIndication::kSwitch;
38}

42constexpr int ScalabilityStructureL2T2KeyShift::kNumSpatialLayers;
43constexpr int ScalabilityStructureL2T2KeyShift::kNumTemporalLayers;
44
45ScalabilityStructureL2T2KeyShift::~ScalabilityStructureL2T2KeyShift() = default;
46
47ScalableVideoController::StreamLayersConfig
48ScalabilityStructureL2T2KeyShift::StreamConfig() const {
49 StreamLayersConfig result;
50 result.num_spatial_layers = 2;
51 result.num_temporal_layers = 2;
52 result.scaling_factor_num[0] = 1;
53 result.scaling_factor_den[0] = 2;
54 return result;
55}
56
57FrameDependencyStructure ScalabilityStructureL2T2KeyShift::DependencyStructure()
58 const {
59 FrameDependencyStructure structure;
60 structure.num_decode_targets = 4;
61 structure.num_chains = 2;
62 structure.decode_target_protected_by_chain = {0, 0, 1, 1};
63 structure.templates.resize(7);
64 auto& templates = structure.templates;
65 templates[0].S(0).T(0).Dtis("SSSS").ChainDiffs({0, 0});
66 templates[1].S(0).T(0).Dtis("SS--").ChainDiffs({2, 1}).FrameDiffs({2});
67 templates[2].S(0).T(0).Dtis("SS--").ChainDiffs({4, 1}).FrameDiffs({4});
68 templates[3].S(0).T(1).Dtis("-D--").ChainDiffs({2, 3}).FrameDiffs({2});
69 templates[4].S(1).T(0).Dtis("--SS").ChainDiffs({1, 1}).FrameDiffs({1});
70 templates[5].S(1).T(0).Dtis("--SS").ChainDiffs({3, 4}).FrameDiffs({4});
71 templates[6].S(1).T(1).Dtis("---D").ChainDiffs({1, 2}).FrameDiffs({2});
72 return structure;
73}
74
75std::vector<ScalableVideoController::LayerFrameConfig>
76ScalabilityStructureL2T2KeyShift::NextFrameConfig(bool restart) {
77 std::vector<LayerFrameConfig> configs;
78 configs.reserve(2);
79 if (restart) {
80 next_pattern_ = kKey;
81 }
82
83 // Buffer0 keeps latest S0T0 frame,
84 // Buffer1 keeps latest S1T0 frame.
85 switch (next_pattern_) {
86 case kKey:
87 if (DecodeTargetIsActive(/*sid=*/0, /*tid=*/0)) {
88 configs.emplace_back();
89 configs.back().S(0).T(0).Update(0).Keyframe();
90 }
91 if (DecodeTargetIsActive(/*sid=*/1, /*tid=*/0)) {
92 configs.emplace_back();
93 configs.back().S(1).T(0).Update(1);
94 if (DecodeTargetIsActive(/*sid=*/0, /*tid=*/0)) {
95 configs.back().Reference(0);
96 } else {
97 configs.back().Keyframe();
98 }
99 }
100 next_pattern_ = kDelta0;
101 break;
102 case kDelta0:
103 if (DecodeTargetIsActive(/*sid=*/0, /*tid=*/0)) {
104 configs.emplace_back();
105 configs.back().S(0).T(0).ReferenceAndUpdate(0);
106 }
107 if (DecodeTargetIsActive(/*sid=*/1, /*tid=*/1)) {
108 configs.emplace_back();
109 configs.back().S(1).T(1).Reference(1);
110 }
111 if (configs.empty() && DecodeTargetIsActive(/*sid=*/1, /*tid=*/0)) {
112 configs.emplace_back();
113 configs.back().S(1).T(0).ReferenceAndUpdate(1);
114 }
115 next_pattern_ = kDelta1;
116 break;
117 case kDelta1:
118 if (DecodeTargetIsActive(/*sid=*/0, /*tid=*/1)) {
119 configs.emplace_back();
120 configs.back().S(0).T(1).Reference(0);
121 }
122 if (DecodeTargetIsActive(/*sid=*/1, /*tid=*/0)) {
123 configs.emplace_back();
124 configs.back().S(1).T(0).ReferenceAndUpdate(1);
125 }
126 if (configs.empty() && DecodeTargetIsActive(/*sid=*/0, /*tid=*/0)) {
127 configs.emplace_back();
128 configs.back().S(0).T(0).ReferenceAndUpdate(0);
129 }
130 next_pattern_ = kDelta0;
131 break;
132 }
133
134 RTC_DCHECK(!configs.empty() || active_decode_targets_.none());
135 return configs;
136}
137
138GenericFrameInfo ScalabilityStructureL2T2KeyShift::OnEncodeDone(
139 const LayerFrameConfig& config) {
140 GenericFrameInfo frame_info;
141 frame_info.spatial_id = config.SpatialId();
142 frame_info.temporal_id = config.TemporalId();
143 frame_info.encoder_buffers = config.Buffers();
144 for (int sid = 0; sid < kNumSpatialLayers; ++sid) {
145 for (int tid = 0; tid < kNumTemporalLayers; ++tid) {
146 frame_info.decode_target_indications.push_back(Dti(sid, tid, config));
147 }
148 }
149 if (config.IsKeyframe()) {
150 frame_info.part_of_chain = {true, true};
151 } else if (config.TemporalId() == 0) {
152 frame_info.part_of_chain = {config.SpatialId() == 0,
153 config.SpatialId() == 1};
154 } else {
155 frame_info.part_of_chain = {false, false};
156 }
157 return frame_info;
158}
159
160void ScalabilityStructureL2T2KeyShift::OnRatesUpdated(
161 const VideoBitrateAllocation& bitrates) {
162 for (int sid = 0; sid < kNumSpatialLayers; ++sid) {
163 // Enable/disable spatial layers independetely.
164 bool active = bitrates.GetBitrate(sid, /*tid=*/0) > 0;
165 if (!DecodeTargetIsActive(sid, /*tid=*/0) && active) {
166 // Key frame is required to reenable any spatial layer.
167 next_pattern_ = kKey;
168 }
169
170 SetDecodeTargetIsActive(sid, /*tid=*/0, active);
171 SetDecodeTargetIsActive(sid, /*tid=*/1,
172 active && bitrates.GetBitrate(sid, /*tid=*/1) > 0);
173 }
174}
